'''BBC威爾斯總部大樓'''（{{Lang-en|BBC Wales Headquarters building}}，{{Lang-cy|Pencadlys BBC Cymru}}）<ref name="NewBuild">{{cite web|url=https://dcfw.org/central-square-bbc-wales-headquarters-building-oct-2014/|title=Central Square & BBC Wales Headquarters Building (Sept 14)|publisher=Design Commission for Wales|accessdate=28 September 2017|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821202249/https://dcfw.org/central-square-bbc-wales-headquarters-building-oct-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[BBC威爾斯|BBC威爾斯]]的總部大樓，也是[[S4C|S4C]]的辦公地點<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-50117558|title=BBC Wales staff start move to new headquarters|date=2019-10-21|access-date=2020-01-11|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191028232241/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-50117558|dead-url=no}}</ref>，位于英国[[威尔士|威尔士]]首府[[加迪夫|加迪夫]]，邻近[[加迪夫中央車站|加迪夫中央車站]]。該建築耗資1.2億英鎊，取代[[廣播大樓_(卡地夫)|卡地夫廣播大樓]]成為BBC威爾斯的新總部<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/business/business-news/first-images-inside-bbc-wales-13300394|title=First images inside BBC Wales' new £120m headquarters in the centre of Cardiff|work=Wales Online|date=2017-07-07|accessdate=2017-09-25|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925181548/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/business/business-news/first-images-inside-bbc-wales-13300394|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年7月15日，BBC威爾斯分部正式入驻總部大樓。<ref>{{cite news |title=BBC Wales Central Square studios in Cardiff go live |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-53420795 |accessdate=2020-08-31 |publisher=英国广播公司 |date=2020-07-15 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829005643/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-53420795 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
